Html:
Is there any documentation put together for the source code? Something like an architecture overview would be nice, but I'd settle for just about anything. :)

I don't know yet if I'd have the time to contribute, but I'd like to poke around a bit at least;

The /Base/Calculations.cs file contains the CalculationsBase class, which is the sort of center of the Rawr work, and it's heavily commented. The first page of the Rawr thread on EJ is also rich in design/architecture descriptions.
